key purpose
  - recieve external messages
  - send messages to kernel by bus
tips
  - interface of the ear
  - who stores the message(if processing is not so fast)
  - the strategy of queue size controlling
  - the strategy of speed of sending messages
  - status of the module
event
  (passive)
  - push message(extern -> ear)
  - fetch message(ear -> kernel)
  
  - get queue size
  - set queue size
  - clear queue

  - open logging
  - close logging
  - get logging level
  - set logging level
  
  - enable auto-send message
  - set send message interval
  - disable auto-send message
  
  - get processed message count
  - get dropped message count
  - get recieved message count

  (active)
  - push message(ear->kernel)
  